<p class="skru-srv-desc">AI support agents that resolve tickets, escalate edge cases, and learn from your knowledge base — reducing support costs by up to 80%.</p>
<ul class="skru-srv-links"><li><a href="/services/ai/intelligent-chatbot-integration-for-smbs/">AI Customer Support Agent</a></li><li><a href="/services/ai/intelligent-chatbot-integration-for-smbs/">Automated Ticket Classification</a></li><li><a href="/services/ai/automated-customer-faq-systems/">AI Knowledge Base Builder</a></li><li><a href="/services/ai/automated-feedback-review-collection/">Customer Sentiment Analysis</a></li></ul></div><div class="skru-srv-card">
<div class="skru-srv-card-top"><div class="skru-srv-icon-wrap"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#51be89" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg></div><h3 class="skru-srv-title">Custom AI Development</h3></div>
<p class="skru-srv-desc">Need something that doesn't exist off the shelf? We design and build bespoke AI agents, RAG systems, and LLM-powered tools for your exact use case.</p>
